DirFool 2.40
By Chris Lawrence


@node WhatsDF "What is DirFool?"
What is DirFool?

@{fg highlight}DirFool@{fg text} (DF) is a small (10.5k) utility that, when using AmigaDOS
2.04, replaces the Dir and List commands with a single command.  DF
has several different operating modes and can work in a used-defined
manner.
@endnode


