BindMonitor.info           CLI
dfformat                   DiskCopy
diskinfowb                 FixFonts
Format                     Format-HD
Format.info                formatHDs
Fountain.info              Install-HD
installHDs                 NoFastMem
prep                       RexxMast
Setmap
148041 bytes used - 3168768 bytes free on volume


@{fg highlight}System2.0:>@{fg text} DF SYS:Tools/~(#?.info) LIST DATE

System2.0:Tools on 15-Jun-92 at 23:03:23
<DIR> Commodities                    ----rwed 13-Apr-92
Fed                            29384 ----rwed 06-Jan-92
